WEBVTT

1
00:27:50.100 --> 00:27:51.880 
不  他的记忆不是被搅乱
No, his memories weren't jumbled.

2
00:27:52.130 --> 00:27:54.040 
而是被...置换了
They were...replaced.

3
00:27:54.140 --> 00:27:55.450 
有一部分被置换了
Just some of them.

4
00:27:56.940 --> 00:27:57.740 
该你了
You're up.

5
00:27:57.770 --> 00:27:59.270 
-不用了  -来吧
- No, I'm okay. - Nah, come on.

6
00:27:59.270 --> 00:28:00.310 
这对你有帮助
It's good for you.

7
00:28:00.510 --> 00:28:02.640 
能训练你大脑和手的协调性
Helps your brain and hands learn to get their act together.

8
00:28:05.380 --> 00:28:07.380 
被置换的记忆  被搅乱的记忆
Replaced memories, jumbled memories...

9
00:28:07.390 --> 00:28:09.550 
他怎么还能保持清醒
How the hell is he supposed to keep everything together?

10
00:28:09.700 --> 00:28:11.220 
要是他忘了他是哪边的人了呢
What if he forgets what team he's on?

11
00:28:11.220 --> 00:28:14.180 
我希望我的老大不要乱糟糟的
You know, I like my bosses un-jumbled at all times.

12
00:28:14.180 --> 00:28:16.060 
他没有乱糟糟的  会好的
Yeah, he is, or he will be.

13
00:28:17.000 --> 00:28:18.480 
他会恢复的  他以前就恢复过
He'll recover. He did before.

14
00:28:19.130 --> 00:28:21.880 
而且大脑永远不会删除文件
Besides, brains never delete files.

15
00:28:21.880 --> 00:28:23.270 
它们只是失去了联系
They just lose connections.

